---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { contact } from "../data/contact";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | EWaste Kochi"
  description="Privacy policy and data handling practices for EWaste Kochi."
>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 prose prose-invert">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: April 2026</p>
    <p>
      At EWaste Kochi, we take data privacy seriously. This policy outlines how
      we handle information collected via our website and our professional data
      destruction services.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Destruction Standards</h2>
    <p>
      For all clients, we adhere to NIST 800-88 R1 standards. Any personal data
      contained on physical media entrusted to us is destroyed irrecoverably
      before hardware recycling or remarketing.
    </p>

    <h2>Website Data</h2>
    <p>
      We collect minimal data via our contact forms and WhatsApp links to
      facilitate pickups. We do not sell or share your contact information with
      third-party marketers.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      For questions regarding your data or to request a Certificate of
      Destruction, contact us at {contact.email}.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
